description: Bringing you an all-new style unlike anything you've ever had, the Zodiac Grill is serving up something special today! American fusion that's perfect for any time of day, this food truck is to be perfect for any and every event. Ready and waiting to satisfy your cravings, Cali Smokehouse Zodiac Grill is here to make sure you'll love every bite of their fantastic food!
name: The Zodiac Grill
